INSERT INTO `amz200k` VALUES (1,'2013-08-09',4,'Surprisingly comfortable','[[\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Women\', \'Clothing\', \'Lingerie, Sleep & Lounge\', \'Intimates\', \'Bras\', \'Everyday Bras\'], [\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Women\', \'Plus-Size\', \'Intimates\', \'Bras\', \'Everyday Bras\']]','This bra help up my extra large girls (44DDD) really well especially since there is no underwire.  The fit was true to size which was another excellent feature.  The only drawback is when those 18 hours come along it starts getting a little uncomfortable, but for it\'s time for bed anyway.  I am very happy with this bra and the comfort straps really are comfortable.I would recommend this, especially for full figured gals who are tired of underwires stabbing them.','I342631873'),(2,'2014-03-18',5,'happy','[[\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Women\'], [\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Novelty, Costumes & More\', \'Novelty\', \'Clothing\', \'Women\', \'Hoodies\']]','nice look..its a 2 n 1 sweater..color is nice...price was very affordable also...i really enjoyed the compliments i received when i wore it......','I367609494'),(3,'2013-09-25',5,'Great hosiery','[[\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Women\'], [\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Novelty, Costumes & More\', \'Exotic Apparel\']]','I bought these to go with a bustier with garter and they were a perfect fit.  Even after one of my bustier garter clasps broke, I could still wear these with the bustier because of the rubber inside the top.  They stay up perfectly.  My husband LOVES touching my legs in these things so I plan on getting a few more pairs to have as needed.','I135310003'),(4,'2013-06-11',4,'Cute Shoes','[[\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Baby\', \'Baby Girls\', \'Shoes\', \'Sneakers\'], [\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Baby\', \'Baby Boys\', \'Shoes\', \'Sneakers\']]','Very cute. Seem a little on the larger side, but that\'s better than smaller. Easy to slip on and off and stay on feet.','I495361067'),(5,'2014-04-19',5,'Great buy','[[\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Women\', \'Handbags & Wallets\', \'Cross-Body Bags\']]','I never bought anything from this brand before but I will certainly buy from them again. I love it, it\'s a great casual every day bag, it\'s exactly what I wanted. Its great quality.','I661706123'),(6,'2014-04-10',5,'Comfortable','[[\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Women\', \'Clothing\', \'Shorts\', \'Casual\']]','Comfortable shorts to do yoga in. Have no issues with them slipping down as others have mentioned. Wear them to class a couple times a week and couldn\'t be happier.','I330290793'),(7,'2012-05-12',5,'Another Wonderful Shoe from Dansko','[[\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Shoes & Accessories: International Shipping Available\'], [\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'D\', \'Dansko\'], [\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Women\', \'Shoes\', \'Fashion Sneakers\']]','I ordered these for the balance between looks and comfort and they do not disappoint. Cute enough to be worn with casual summer dresses and skirt they are sturdy enough and comfortable enough to make walking long distances appealing. The same with standing for long periods. There is a reason that so many nurses and doctors wear the standard Dansko Clog.These do look like the little summer sneakers we love to wear around. Dansko quality is also unmatched. I own 2 pairs of clogs and a pair of boots by Dansko, all of which have lasted years and all of which still look well and are comfortable when worn. Worth the investment. I see from some reviews that some people with foot problems don\'t like these. Not every shoe is for everybody. Most people love Dansko, so give their ergonomic foot bed and arch support a try and see if it works with your foot. Highest possible recommendation.','I284382593'),(8,'2013-12-10',5,'Cute Boots','[[\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'U\', \'UGG\'], [\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Women\', \'Shoes\', \'Boots\']]','I chose this rating because I like them. My 18 year old granddaughter has asked for them for Christmas, (she doesn\'t know I have them.) She has worn UGG\'s before, so I know she will love them. As usual, the service from Amazon Prime has been prompt and I love the updates.','I251191438'),(9,'2014-07-09',4,'But I will use them as a good comfortable walking shoes','[[\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Shoes & Accessories: International Shipping Available\'], [\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'G\', \'Grasshoppers\'], [\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Women\', \'Shoes\', \'Athletic\', \'Walking\']]','The shoes fit and soft. But I wish the look is more youthful.They look rather &#34;Granny&#34; . But I will use them as a good comfortable walking shoes.','I437530446'),(10,'2013-12-31',4,'Looks exactly like the photo','[[\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Women\', \'Clothing\', \'Tops & Tees\', \'Blouses & Button-Down Shirts\']]','My shirt arrived today and it looks just like the photo, the photo itself gives off the slight impression that the sleeves look like silk or something similar, this is not true. Just to let you know, the sleeves on the item are cloth and made of a stretchy material. I really like the way it fits, i take a size Large in shirts these days and i ordered an XL just to be safe, it fits well, all in all i am very happy with this purchase. And ordering a size up payed off, the shirt fits perfectly.','I775395395'),(11,'2013-12-05',5,'Great school bag','[[\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'N\', \'Nine West\'], [\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Women\', \'Handbags & Wallets\', \'Top-Handle Bags\'], [\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Women\', \'Handbags & Wallets\', \'Shoulder Bags\']]','I\'m a graduate student, and I\'ve been using this as my school bag for two quarters & a summer so far! It fits: my Macbook 13&#34; Air in a neoprene case, thin folders, my Kleen Kanteen, wallet, snack, cell phone, lotion, and assorted personal items -- basically, everything I need for a full day of school!This bag can take a lot of weight, and it\'s held up really well. Because of the way the handles are wrapped and the material, it doesn\'t seem like I\'ll need to worry about fraying handles (what killed my other school bags). The only thing is that the black band around the lock fell off after about 6 months of use, but I just chipped the glue off with the edge of a steel ruler, and it looks fine.I recommend it!','I915012432'),(12,'2013-11-01',5,'fit, quality review','[[\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Men\', \'Clothing\', \'Shirts\', \'T-Shirts\']]','Tee shirt is awesome, heavy weight, quality material, true to size: boxy men\'s fit. Clean and simple lines, well made, thick stitching and the absolute best prices on the planet. These are not Hanes or Fruit of the Looms, more like Costco or higher end tee\'s. Buy several. My husband is 6\'4, 200lbs, XL is slightly too large, my friend is 6\', 215 lbs, the xl fits him perfectly.','I065416460'),(13,'2014-05-08',5,'Lots of compliments','[[\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Women\', \'Clothing\', \'Tops & Tees\', \'Blouses & Button-Down Shirts\'], [\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Women\', \'Plus-Size\', \'Tops & Tees\', \'Blouses & Button-Down Shirts\']]','When you wear this you get lots and lots of compliments.  It is a beautiful and comfortable shirt. Love the color too','I627533415'),(14,'2014-05-20',5,'VERY GIRLIE!  JUST LIKE MOI!!','[[\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Women\', \'Clothing\', \'Dresses\', \'Casual\']]','The dress is thicker (more layers) than I thought.  Which is just great, I\'m not complaining!  Can\'t wait for MN weather to hurry up and warm up so I can wear the dress!!!','I492708565'),(15,'2014-01-18',5,'Perfect','[[\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Men\', \'Accessories\', \'Hats & Caps\', \'Skullies & Beanies\']]','Exactly what I wanted. Great price, arrived quickly, quality and color are fantastic. Keeps my head nice and warm. I been getting compliments from everyone about it and they ask where I got it.','I765454203'),(16,'2014-06-05',5,'Great belt.','[[\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Men\', \'Accessories\', \'Belts\']]','Great quality leather belt which I like for everyday wear. While this belt is not the type I would wear for with a suit or other than with casual clothes it is attractive and presents itself well.  Sizing is accurate and for the cost is totally outstanding.','I817012574'),(17,'2014-06-07',5,'Love these shoes!','[[\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Women\', \'Shoes\', \'Loafers & Slip-Ons\']]','I usually wear a 6.5, but I got a 7, I had the feeling I needed to go up in size and I was correct. These shoes go with everything and are very comfortable. They are kind of pricey though.','I419667688'),(18,'2014-06-15',5,'Great for nursing!','[[\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Women\', \'Clothing\', \'Tops & Tees\', \'Tanks & Camis\'], [\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Women\', \'Maternity\']]','This tank is great for nursing especially after you get home from the hospital. Very comfortable and gives you enough room for your tummy that is still decreasing in size.','I224319655'),(19,'2014-02-20',5,'Good Quality','[[\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Shoes & Accessories: International Shipping Available\'], [\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Winter Promo\'], [\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'B\', \'Bearpaw\'], [\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Boot Shop\', \'Women\', \'Fashion\', \'Shearling\'], [\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Women\', \'Shoes\', \'Boots\']]','My daughter loves these boots! They are good quality, warm, comfortable and much more affordable than UGGS.You will not be disappointed in purchasing these.','I231748133'),(20,'2013-07-22',5,'Love this!','[[\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Shoes & Accessories: International Shipping Available\'], [\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'S\', \'Sam Edelman\'], [\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Boot Shop\', \'Women\', \'Fashion\', \'Western\'], [\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Women\', \'Shoes\', \'Boots\']]','This boot are the most fashion product I ever bought. It is really special, I use it with jeans and love them!','I849950022'),(21,'2013-09-20',4,'Skechers Shoes','[[\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Shoes & Accessories: International Shipping Available\'], [\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'S\', \'Skechers\'], [\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Comfort Shoes\'], [\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Women\', \'Shoes\', \'Fashion Sneakers\']]','Well the wife ordered this pair of shoes for work. she had to wait a long time to get em however it was worth the wait. the shoes are comfortable as well as durable.','I630819604'),(22,'2013-12-10',5,'Best boot I own','[[\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Shoes & Accessories: International Shipping Available\'], [\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'C\', \'Clarks\'], [\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Comfort Shoes\'], [\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Women\', \'Shoes\', \'Boots\']]','I love love love these Clark boots. Great quality and comfort. Has become my new favorite boot! I will keep my eye opened for Clark boots going forward.','I890943132'),(23,'2014-02-03',5,'great shoe','[[\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Women\', \'Shoes\', \'Outdoor\', \'Rain Footwear\']]','Got these for gift to sister moving to seattle  she wears them every day looooooves them and they were super comfy and true to size.','I545987364'),(24,'2013-05-24',5,'A very cool and subtle image','[[\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Men\'], [\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Novelty, Costumes & More\', \'Band & Music Fan\', \'T-Shirts\'], [\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Novelty, Costumes & More\', \'Movie & TV Fan\', \'Tops & Tees\', \'T-Shirts\']]','I love the subdued image of Michonne flanked by the zombies. Really quite beautiful...in its own macabre way.I should have bought 1 size larger as the large, just isn\'t.','I678259832'),(25,'2013-11-12',4,'Love the lace','[[\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Women\', \'Clothing\', \'Lingerie, Sleep & Lounge\', \'Intimates\', \'Bras\', \'Everyday Bras\'], [\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Women\', \'Plus-Size\']]','This bra fits true to size (maaaaybe a hair small in the cup, but barely), is comfortable, and looks good on.  The lace is a nice touch that makes it look really cute and sexy.Always hand-wash and hang- or flat-dry your bras with detergent meant for delicates!  Otherwise you\'re throwing your money away.','I697204909'),(26,'2012-12-17',5,'Great for those days!','[[\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Men\', \'Clothing\', \'Jeans\']]','Love the material and the color. Sizing is what I guess is current standards. The sizes of jeans are a changing. Found that they are great for those days when you don\'t want something on that is a snug as Slim Straights, which is what I generally wear. There is plenty of room to move without swimming in them. Great jeans for the money!','I018499161'),(27,'2013-12-05',5,'Finally!!!! A sandal that I can walk in','[[\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Shoes & Accessories: International Shipping Available\'], [\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'N\', \'Naturalizer\'], [\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Comfort Shoes\'], [\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Women\', \'Shoes\', \'Sandals\']]','I was heading to Australia and wanted a sandal that would match everything and was comfortable to walk in.  This sandal did not disappoint.  It was wonderful.  Comfortable, good support, and matched everything.  I received several compliments on this sandal.  Will purchase a fresh pair for next summer but will get it in at least three colors','I307043064'),(28,'2014-03-05',3,'Small cups','[[\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Women\', \'Clothing\', \'Lingerie, Sleep & Lounge\', \'Intimates\', \'Bras\', \'Everyday Bras\'], [\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Women\', \'Petite\', \'Intimates\', \'Bras\', \'Everyday Bras\'], [\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Women\', \'Plus-Size\']]','The cups size is a bit small. I purchased what I normally would and there is still a little bulging on the top.','I364077569'),(29,'2013-10-14',1,'The worst purchase on amazon i\'ve ever made! DONT BUY IT!','[[\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Women\', \'Clothing\', \'Dresses\', \'Night Out & Cocktail\']]','This dress is simply horrible! the material is too thin, the quality is poor, fits bad, it looks so much better on the picture, but when I received it i was extremely disappointed. I\'ve purchased lots of clothing for such price or even cheaper, but i\'ve never had such a disappointment!','I304017335'),(30,'2010-06-11',5,'Perfect!','[[\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Men\', \'Accessories\', \'Suspenders\']]','i couldn\'t find white suspenders anywhere but of course the amazing amazon.com has them!! I feel weird buying clothes online but i was wanting them for my hubby-to-be to wear at the wedding so bad! so after reading the other reviews i had to ask myself....will they last one day of crazy dancing and matrimony? Yes They do! the straps are alittle smaller than i have see before but i love them and so does my hubby....a tip for the ladies- they can also be used as a sexy prop on the wedding night! hehe','I697163779'),(31,'2013-08-23',5,'Quality','[[\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'D\', \'Dickies\'], [\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Boys\', \'Clothing\', \'Tops & Tees\', \'Polos\'], [\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Boys\', \'School Uniforms\', \'Clothing\', \'Tops\']]','You can\'t go wrong for the money . I have ordered more and my son loves the one he has now. He is excited to get the new ones.','I188941974'),(32,'2013-12-04',4,'Should be fine','[[\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Women\', \'Shoes\', \'Flats\']]','I bought these to take on a cruise.  They\'re lightweight, the grey color will &#34;go with&#34; almost everything, and they were inexpensive enough that if they take a beating throughout the vacation, they can be disposable.  The workmanship isn\'t great, but that\'s OK for the reason I ordered them  Haven\'t worn them for a length of time yet, but after trying them on I expect they\'ll be comfortable.  I feel they were a smart buy for my purpose.Earlier I bought the same shoe in a half-size larger (6-1/2) in the suede look.  They were enormous.  I\'ll keep them, anyhow, to wear around the house.','I686693620'),(33,'2012-12-08',4,'great shoe','[[\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Shoes & Accessories: International Shipping Available\'], [\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'K\', \'Keen\'], [\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Comfort Shoes\'], [\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Men\', \'Shoes\', \'Oxfords\']]','I\'ve had these shoes for 6 months, wearing 2-4 days per week, as a contractor.  They feel great.  They are easily the most comfortable shoe I have worn in years, and my feet are getting harder to please. The all leather upper is a plus.  The shoe looks good.  The moc toe is a bit of a minus for me, as the stitching around the toe has failed due to the punishment I put the shoe through.  I easily fixed the problem, to my surprise, with some waxed thread and a needle in about 15 minutes.  The repair looks good as new, and will outlast the shoe.  They are a bit on the warm side, but tolerable.  The sole is wearing well.  I will look for another pair when these finally wear out.','I969811804'),(34,'2014-07-12',5,'love','[[\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Women\'], [\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Novelty, Costumes & More\', \'Novelty\']]','Love it..i always get compliments when i wear it','I133970656'),(35,'2012-10-16',3,'Pretty but not functional','[[\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Women\', \'Shoes\', \'Mules & Clogs\']]','This shoe does not provide the support I have become accustomed to from other Orthaheel shoes I have purchased.  It is okay for short distance walking and sitting. It is quite soft and does not help with heel pain or foot support.  I have only worn them once.  I put them on after I got to my office.  I could not walk around in them too much because my heel began to hurt.  If I had not worn them, I would have returned them.','I275097306'),(36,'2014-02-23',4,'LOVE THESE!!!!','[[\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Women\', \'Plus-Size\', \'Jeans\'], [\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Novelty, Costumes & More\', \'Novelty\', \'Clothing\', \'Women\', \'Leggings\']]','These are by far my favourite leggings, I just wish the waistband was 100x better. It doesn\'t fit tightly so it sags.','I874288210'),(37,'2014-02-06',4,'PRETTY','[[\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Women\'], [\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Novelty, Costumes & More\', \'Novelty\', \'Jewelry\', \'Necklaces & Pendants\']]','I LIKE THIS, IT LOOKS VERY VINTAGE. I LIKE THE COLORS AND THE PEACOCK. I HAVEN\'T WORN IT YET, BUT PLAN ON IT.','I003716158'),(38,'2014-04-10',1,'see thru','[[\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Women\', \'Clothing\', \'Dresses\']]','I can see right thru this. I wasnt a fan of the sleeves either but I did recieve the belt which is pretty cute. Soooo thats cool, right?','I815510638'),(39,'2014-03-06',5,'Merino','[[\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Men\', \'Clothing\', \'Underwear\', \'Thermal Underwear\', \'Tops\']]','I never knew about Merino until my recent trip to New York.  I grew up thinking that all wool products were itchy and uncomfortable.  After wearing Merino, I don\'t think that I could ever go back to the synthetics like BodyArmor and other brands employ.  The Merino kept me warm when out in the freezing temperatures of New York but cool enough to wear indoors with the heater on, too -- Hell, I have worn it on several early morning hikes after returning to Arizona.  Extremely comfortable and doesn\'t pill when washed like another merino shirt that I ordered.','I516546542'),(40,'2013-11-24',5,'Warmth at a good price','[[\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Shoes & Accessories: International Shipping Available\'], [\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'E\', \'EMU Australia\'], [\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Boot Shop\', \'Women\', \'Fashion\', \'Shearling\'], [\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry