ng is better than this shoe for the above functions. If someone is not happy with this shoe they are being overly precious.Unlike a lot of reviewers I have flat feet so I need to be very astute when buying shoes because if not designed correctly they are complete waste of money. I am lucky that I can afford to spent thousands on shoes to find the right shoe and I have purchase all if not most of the major brands. After spending many thousands all roads lead back to Saloman.This shoe is awesome, the feel, the fit, the design, the construction all scream quality. When I exercise in them they hold my foot in a neutral position and I don\'t over pronate which is a sign of quality for someone with rubbish feet like myself.In my opinion the true test of a shoe is not how shoes function with good feet, its how they function with people was bad feet. If you have high arches you can run bare feet or in just about any shoe, but not with people with very flat feet.If you are on the fence with these shoes just get them.','I391842100'),(738,'2014-01-23',3,'It\'s not enough good','[[\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'C\', \'Calvin Klein\'], [\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Men\', \'Clothing\', \'Sleep & Lounge\', \'Sleep Bottoms\']]','Beautiful and comfortable, but you expect it to be better, you used and washed twice and now change, expected to be the longest-old','I108155316'),(739,'2014-05-13',4,'Fleece Coat','[[\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Women\', \'Clothing\', \'Coats & Jackets\', \'Trench & Rain\']]','I really do like this coat. It looks amazing and is very comfortable. I wish the coat was a bit tighter though. I ordered a medium. If I was to of ordered a small the length of the arms would of probable been to short. Customer Service is also very helpful. Great price for this coat defiantly worth it!','I147541788'),(740,'2013-12-31',5,'good','[[\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Girls\'], [\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Novelty, Costumes & More\', \'Novelty\']]','im so g